testcase.name: reframedFlow: chunks containing exactly one message should pass through
reframedFlow: chunks containing fragments of messages should be re-assembled
reframedFlow: reject an input stream that is completed in the middle of a frame
reintroduceOrdering: pass through a sorted stream directly
isNotified: always notify users of broadcast messages
isNotified: notify the followers of an user that updates his status
eventsFlow: downstream should receive completion when the event source is completed
incomingDataFlow: reframe, reorder and compute followers
outgoingFlow: filter out events that should not be delivered to the given user
